data.description: Nice home located in a beautiful area of Okmulgee. This 3 bedroom home has had many updates and has tons of charm and character. Large living room with fire place, Nice screened in sun rooms both up & downstairs , New roof in September 2019, Tank less hot water heater & new paint thru out are just a a few of the special amenities in this home. All bedrooms are upstairs with large walk-in closets and lots of windows. Corner lot with mature trees and fenced back yard. This property has been virtually staged
